<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>OpenZero // Operations Manual</title>
    <style>
        body { background: #000; color: #fff; font-family: 'Courier New', monospace; padding: 40px; text-transform: uppercase; }
        .container { max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto; }
        .header { border-bottom: 2px solid #00ff41; padding-bottom: 20px; margin-bottom: 40px; }
        h1 { color: #00ff41; margin: 0; font-size: 2.5em; letter-spacing: -2px; }
        .box { border: 1px solid #222; background: #050505; padding: 30px; margin-bottom: 40px; }
        h2 { color: #00ff41; font-size: 1.2em; margin-top: 0; }
        table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin-top: 20px; }
        th, td { border: 1px solid #222; padding: 15px; text-align: left; }
        th { background: #111; color: #00ff41; }
        .back { color: #fff; text-decoration: none; border: 1px solid #444; padding: 10px 20px; display: inline-block; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .back:hover { border-color: #00ff41; color: #00ff41; }
        .cmd { color: #00ff41; font-weight: bold; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <a href="/" class="back"><< EXIT_TO_DASHBOARD</a>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>TACTICAL OPERATIONS MANUAL v4.0</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="box">
        <h2>01 // STARTUP SEQUENCE</h2>
        <p>After running the installer, navigate to the project root and execute the launcher:</p>
        <code style="display:block; background:#000; padding:15px; border:1px solid #333;">cd ~/openzero && ./start_openzero_ui.sh</code>
        <p>Dashboard Access: <strong>http://localhost:1024</strong></p>
    </div>

    <div class="box">
        <h2>02 // CORE COMMAND SYNTAX</h2>
        <table>
            <tr><th>OBJECTIVE</th><th>COMMAND</th></tr>
            <tr><td>OS Terminal Control</td><td><span class="cmd">run [command]</span></td></tr>
            <tr><td>Activate Vision</td><td><span class="cmd">go to [url]</span></td></tr>
            <tr><td>Remote Server SSH</td><td><span class="cmd">ssh [IP] [USER] [CMD]</span></td></tr>
            <tr><td>RAG Knowledge Search</td><td><span class="cmd">explain [topic]</span></td></tr>
        </table>
    </div>

    <div class="box">
        <h2>03 // SYSTEM LOGS</h2>
        <p>The bottom panel in Mission Control provides real-time feedback from the Python Brain and Moltbot Hand. If a command fails, check this terminal for the raw system output.</p>
    </div>

    <footer style="color:#222; text-align:center; margin-top:50px;">
        CONFIDENTIAL // OPENZERO OPS // 2026
    </footer>
</div>
</body>
</html>
